---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Projects | Mohammad Abu Huzaifa"
  description="Selected data analytics projects: dashboards, EDA, predictive insights, and reporting."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Projects</h1>
  <p class="mt-2 text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
    A curated selection of analytics and dashboard projects with clear problem framing, approach, and outcomes.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="https://github.com/HUZAIFA1610/Water-Quality-Prediction-Maintenance-Service" target="_blank">
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Featured</div>
      <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">Water Quality Prediction & Maintenance</div>
      <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Predictive analytics + risk alerts for maintenance scheduling.
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-sky-400">View on GitHub →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="https://github.com/HUZAIFA1610/Ecommerce-Sales-Dashboard" target="_blank">
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Dashboard</div>
      <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">E-commerce Sales Dashboard</div>
      <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Sales trends, category performance, KPIs (Power BI).
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-sky-400">View on GitHub →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="https://github.com/HUZAIFA1610/Uber-Data-Analysis---R" target="_blank">
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Analysis</div>
      <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">Uber Trip Data Analysis (2014)</div>
      <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Patterns and trends across trips over time (R).
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-sky-400">View on GitHub →</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
    Next: we’ll add your full project list with filters (Dashboard / Analysis / System) and consistent “case-study” layout.
  </p>
</Layout>
